/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Unerwünscht:</strong> Dieses Feature wurde aus den Webstandards entfernt. Obwohl manche Browser es immer noch unterstützen, wird es zukünftig wegfallen. Es sollte daher nicht mehr in alten oder neuen Projekten verwendet werden. Webseiten oder Webapps, die es benutzen, funktionieren möglicherweise irgendwann nicht mehr korrekt.</p></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">Die <strong><code>setYear()</code></strong> Methode setzt das Jahr für eine Datum bezüglich der Ortszeit. Weil <code>setYear()</code> nicht das volle Jahr setzt (\"Jahr 2000 Probem\"), wird es nicht länger eingesetzt und wird von der Methode <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>setFullYear()</code></a> ersetzt.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>dateObj</var>.setYear(<var>yearValue</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"yearvalue\"><code>yearValue</code></dt>\n <dd>Eine ganze Zahl.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Die Anzahl der Millisekunden zwischen dem 1. Januar 1970 00:00:00 UTC und dem geänderten date Objekt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wenn <code>yearValue</code> eine Nummer zwische 0 und 99 (inklusiv) ist, wird das Jahr eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>date</code></a> Objekt mit dem Wert <code>1900 + yearValue</code> gesetzt. Ansernfalls wird das Jahr des Objektes mit dem Wert&nbsp; <code>yearValue</code> gesetzt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_von_setyear()","title":"Einsatz von <code>setYear()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Die ersten beiden Zeilen setzen das Jahr auf 1996. Die dritte Zeile setzt das Jahr auf 2000</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> theBigDay <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">96</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1996</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz von setYear()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%201st%20edition,%20June%201997.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition. Implementiert in JavaScript 1.0.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-B.2.5\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Date.prototype.setYear' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Definiert in dem (informativen) Kompatibilitäts-Anhang</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-date.prototype.setyear\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Date.prototype.setYear' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span>Definiert in</span> dem <span>(normativ)</span> <span>Anhang</span> <span>für</span> <span>zusätzliche Funktionen</span> <span>für Web-Browser</span><span>.</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-date.prototype.setyear\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Date.prototype.setYear' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span>Definiert in</span> dem <span>(normativ)</span> <span>Anhang</span> <span>für</span> <span>zusätzliche Funktionen</span> <span>für Web-Browser</span><span>.</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Date.setYear","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setYear/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getFullYear()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCFullYear()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setFullYear()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCFullYear\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCFullYear()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikat